data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT! ****ASSUMABLE 4.875% MORTGAGE TO THOSE WHO QUALIFY! SAVING YOU HUNDREDS ON YOUR PAYMENT!  BETTER THAN NEW! Don't wait months for a new build when you can have BETTER than new! 1-year-old home with IMMEDIATE OCCUPANCY AND CLEAN! Welcome to your dream Florida oasis! This Palomar model boasts a fabulous floor plan and is a spacious open-concept home that offers the perfect blend of modern luxury and tropical tranquility. This beautiful home offers plenty of room for the whole family or guests with 4 bedrooms and 2.5 baths, ensuring comfort and convenience. The large integrated kitchen-living space provides for a perfect Friday Night Football gathering and entertaining. You will love the Granite countertops and beautiful White cabinets with crown molding, along with a cozy coffee bar. The spacious island gives plenty of area to sit while prepping for your favorite meals. The front family room is ideal for extra dining to host all your family holidays or use it as a sitting room for coffee as you enjoy the morning sun. Large primary bedroom with en-suite and large walk-in closet. The bonus room upstairs can be used in many ways-craft area, office space, and an extra TV area. You will love the UPDGRADED ENTIRE main floor Luxury Plank Flooring, whole house water filtration system, Ring doorbell camera, BRAND NEW refrigerator, YES! The washer and Dryer are being included! large kitchen closet pantry, blinds throughout, and beautiful added landscaping! The spacious yard will be great for your dream pool, outdoor activities, and gardening. Enjoy the community pool, playground, basketball court, dog park, clubhouse, and small recreation area. The Shell Cove community nestled in a peaceful neighborhood, will give you a small-town feel while being centrally located between Tampa and Sarasota and minutes to I-75. Enjoy easy access to top-rated Gulf Coast beaches, world-class golf courses, shopping, and nearby waterfront dining. Shell Cove is located minutes from local area attractions such as Little Harbor, Bahia Beach, and E.G. Simmons Park where you can enjoy fishing, camping, and boating! Also located nearby is the USA TODAY 10Best Readers' Choice Travel Awards for best free attractions at the Manatee Viewing Center. Don't miss out on the incredible opportunity to own this home in this low-inventory market! Florida living at its' finest!
